name: Cara Delevingne
description:
Textual Inversion of Cara Delevingne.

I wasnt happy how SD massacred my girl, so I tried to fix that.

This is my first attempt at doing textual inversion, most of the time I have no clue what Im doing but it turned out well I guess...

Trigger word is caradelevingne_ti.

it is now happily cooked but lowering the weight to 0.98 sometimes does help.

v1 was trained with 7 images for 800 steps

v2 was trained with 8 images for 3000 steps

I tested the TI with some of the most famous prompts from this site, mostly got usable results. Will be improving over time, as I learn more.

Oh and the training data had necklaces and chokers in them so you might want to put that into negative if it generates too much stuff around the neck lol

modelVersions.name: v2 - 1850 steps
modelVersions.description:
retrained with better images and more steps. i checked the pt file with inspect_embedding_training.py and it sits comfortably at 0.1915

hope to see some nice images from you :)
